Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.10,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Things aren’t looking good, Oz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.06,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Ever the optimist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.26,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,While I would not say our current predicament is… ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.42,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I think we can both agree that the situation could be much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.77,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Humanity is a resilient force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:54.95,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oz...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:59.97,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Pro Huntsmen like that don’t just bite it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.06,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Salem’s powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:05.05,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,It seems like her reach is growing by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.22,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,What does that say about humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:13.58,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,That there are indeed a misguided few who have filled their hearts with malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.88,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,It doesn’t take a great number of people to cause harm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:22.27,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,But I still believe there are far more people in this world willing to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:24.94,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.76,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.80,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:29.94,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:33.82,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,We were just about to gather everyone to discuss our next steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.08,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.64,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Something on your mind kiddo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.55,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Uh, it’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.78,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,If it’s okay to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.24,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.58,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Well, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.61,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,We’ve been talking about the Relic at Haven...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.87,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,and the Spring Maiden, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.11,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,...what about the Fall Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.81,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Cinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.37,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Does that mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.94,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Salem has the Beacon Relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.51,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Very astute, Miss Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.32,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I was wondering who would be the first to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.09,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.86,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Thankfully she does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.56,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,It’s true that the Relic at Haven is very much at risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.25,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,and for now, that should remain our primary focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:31.38,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Let’s just say I made finding the Relic at Beacon a… bit more challenging than at the other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.62,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,That’s good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.07,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:41.24,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,But let’s not forget the challenges that still lie before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:49.57,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Now is there anything else we can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.02,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Well, I did have one more question
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.06,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,No, my cane is not a Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.06,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,I have no more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.90,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Yes, while this cane is indeed very precious to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.00,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,it is also just that - 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.37,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.92,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,While I admit it still has a few more tricks up its sleeve,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.26,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I can firmly say that being a Relic isn’t one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.94,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Now why don’t you run and get the other students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.30,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.36,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.91,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, we’ll be there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.88,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.97,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,It was Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.13,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Says he had a breakthrough with the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.52,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinks he might be able to get together a small raiding party for the bandits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:49.74,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,He wants us to meet up at the school tomorrow night to walk us through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.70,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.72,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Oh that’s great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.85,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,I’ll go get the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:04.49,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,That sounds drastically different from your original conversation, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.02,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.46,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:13.02,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Things aren’t looking good, Oz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.16,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.23,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,I still have questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.28,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,You’re not alone in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:33.26,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,You know, I never expected you would be the one to have the guts to betray Oz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.34,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,Which makes me wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.77,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,what does she have on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.70,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,I’m helping her for the same reason you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.42,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,I’m afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.42,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,We…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.57,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,We can’t stop her…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.61,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,No one can…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.76,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,That’s why I tried to leave when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.31,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,I’m not afraid, I’m smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.94,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,You can call it whatever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.73,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,it doesn’t really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.60,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,We’re here…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.27,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,helping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.58,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,I’ve crossed a line…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.32,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,I’ve done things that Ozpin will never forgive, and he shouldn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.08,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,I don’t know where I go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:15.51,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,Man up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.24,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,You did what you had to do to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.35,Default,Raven,0,0,0,,There is no shame in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.18,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,Who are you trying to convince?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.48,Default,Kali,0,0,0,,Do you have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.28,Default,Yuma,0,0,0,,Quiet now…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.14,Default,Guard01,0,0,0,,Ma’am, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.06,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Did you come in here to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.63,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.22,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I didn’t want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.35,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,But you’re still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.85,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I don’t have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.65,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.06,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Just… stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.89,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Why do you feel like we have to hurt people to get our way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.31,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Because it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.47,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,That doesn’t make it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.18,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop lecturing me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.57,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why couldn’t you just leave?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.52,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Because I run away too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:58.98,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Sorry, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.31,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Quit taking potshots and fight me like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.26,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}You used to see things the way I did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.91,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way Adam did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:41.70,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,If no one’s going to do anything to stop the humans that attack us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.11,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,then the only choice we have left…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.11,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}…is to attack back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.18,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You’re wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.20,Default,Blake,0,0,0,, here’s always another choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:07.20,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Ilia…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.43,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.36,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You’re a good person but you’re making all the wrong decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.28,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.84,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Is this really what your parents would’ve wanted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.90,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I don’t know what else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.06,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I don’t know what else to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:39.89,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:42.96,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.76,Default,Fennec,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ilia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.00,Default,Fennec,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:08.83,Default,Fennec,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.12,Default,Fennec,0,0,0,,BROTHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.36,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,Go help Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:41.43,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.57,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.66,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.36,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.47,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.76,Default,Corsac,0,0,0,,{\i1}What have you done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.09,Default,Corsac,0,0,0,,You ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.60,Default,Corsac,0,0,0,,EVERYTHIIIING!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.36,Default,Guard02,0,0,0,,Back! Everyone, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.02,Default,Guard02,0,0,0,,We’ve got people inside doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.50,Default,Faunus01,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.74,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,Get in there! Search for any stragglers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.75,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,We came as soon as we got the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.98,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,And Fennec?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:39.86,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,Was it worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.90,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.16,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Humans didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.52,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,We did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.23,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Faunus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.76,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,We did this to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.34,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,We are just as capable of hate and violence as the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.90,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,but I don't think any of us would jump at the chance to point that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:44.10,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,So why are we letting Adam do it for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:50.79,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}By doing nothing and staying silent, we let others speak and act in our place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:54.58,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,And if we're not proud of the choices they make,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.28,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,then we have no one to blame but ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:05.94,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,This is the message that Adam Taurus will bring to the world if no one stops him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.21,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,But we can stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:15.88,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You have to understand that all of you are looking for simple answers to a very complicated problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.38,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,And I can't give that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.04,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I don't know how to make hate go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.02,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:30.34,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know that this kind of violence is not the solution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.60,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:39.98,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}that to ask you to leave your homes and protect Haven Academy is asking you to put your lives at risk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.86,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,But that's what's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.01,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,So I'm going,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.65,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,and I'll stand by myself if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.07,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll stand with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:00.78,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.57,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,If you’d have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.84,Default,Faunus02,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn’t that the White Fang girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought she hated the Belladonnas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.46,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,You’re not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.48,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let her come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.54,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,You’re just going to forgive her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.59,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,After everything she did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.20,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.22,Default,Saber,0,0,0,,What does she think she’s doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.68,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,She’s learned a lesson that evaded me until I was much older:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.86,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,That there is strength in forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.22,Default,Mata,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.25,Default,YFW,0,0,0,,I’ll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll stand with you! I’ll go!! Yeah!! Me too! Let’s go! Yeah, let’s go!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.63,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,Looks like we’ve got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.34,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.76,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,You stabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:14.93,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:15.53,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.25,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.68,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,Let’s just call it even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.33,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,We have about two weeks before Adam’s attack on Haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:32.32,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,We’re going to need shields, training, whatever we can do to protect as many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.51,Default,Kali,0,0,0,,We’ll need transportation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.74,Default,Kali,0,0,0,,For everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.74,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I think I know a ship captain who owes us a favor.
